page.title: 11A TYPICAL DAY (CONT)
page.content: After football on Thursdays we have a music lesson,then at three thirty it's time to go home.We always sing a prayer at this time of day to thank God for everything.We arrive home at about four,and we have our tea and jam sandwiches.Then I play on my motorbike ,a yamaha 80 c.c. for an hour.Between five and six I do my homework,and half an hour later we sit down for our supper.After supper we watch television until half past eight,then we get ready for bed.I brush my teeth and wash my hands and face,then settle down ready for sleep.I'm usually well away by about nine o'clock.
